In [26]:
import itertools

numerical_columns = df.select_dtypes(include='number').columns

for (x, y) in itertools.combinations(numerical_columns, 2):
    plt.figure(figsize=(4, 3))
    sns.scatterplot(x=x, y=y, data=df)
    plt.title(f'Scatterplot of {x} vs {y}')
    plt.xlabel(x)
    plt.ylabel(y)
    plt.show()
